3.7 The DUIM-OLE-CONTROL module

ocx-frame

Sealed generic function

Summary

Given an instance of <ocx-dispatch> or <DUIM-OCX>, returns the associated DUIM frame.

Signature

ocx-frame interface => frame

Arguments

interface
An instance of <ocx-dispatch> or <DUIM-OCX>.

Values

frame
An instance of <embeddable-frame>.

Library

duim-ole-control

Module

duim-ole-control

Description

Given an instance of <ocx-dispatch> or <DUIM-OCX>, returns the associated DUIM frame.
